1507308-a.folder: Avenue A - 6th Street - 6th Street, northwest corner, Manhattan, NY
1507308-a.title: Avenue A - 6th Street - 6th Street, northwest corner

715859f-a.text:
Avenue A, north from East 6th Street.  At the right is a motion picture house, Loews Hollywood Theatre.  Tompkins Square occupies the entire three blocks to the north. Note the bus service that replaces the former trolley line.  Track removal and surface repavement has been performed by the W.P.A.
										   May 17, 1937

Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
